description:
The story of Elijah, Ahab, and Jezebel has many end-time applications. What lessons can we learn from this story that will prepare us for the end-time crisis?

Jezebel created a surveillance state to monitor and suppress God's people during the time of Elijah. In the end time, worldly powers under the control of Satan will employ a surveillance system to persecute God's church. Satan wants to destroy God's children, but God will not allow him to triumph. When demonic powers reach their height, God intervenes. 
How can God's people protect themselves during the last days? Learn how you can find true security in this lecture by Hal Mayer.
